    "name": "Pyric Harbinger",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Though called \u201cthe spawn of the Eshtayiv,\u201d pyric harbingers are the constituents of this entity rather than its offspring. These rare creatures travel through space to find dark places to illuminate and beings to slay, creating terror and pyric undead.<br/><br/>A pyric harbinger looks like an orb of fire, but within that flame is a gelatinous sphere that is 5 feet in diameter and mostly maw. Those who\u2019ve studied a harbinger\u2019s ashy remains estimate they weigh only 100 pounds."
        }
    ],
